title: Owaisi on dispute over placing idol near dargah: ‘We know bulldozers will be…’ - Hindustan Times
content: Owaisi on dispute over placing idol near dargah: ‘We know bulldozers will be…’  Hindustan Times
description: The two groups on Monday night indulged in arguments and pelted each other with stones, following which the police lobbed teargas shells to disperse them, reported PTI quoting officials.
